data.text:
Haylie Duff and Nick Zano split up last year, but has the actor already moved on to his new co-star?

Reports surfacing say that Zano is dating his ‘Two Broke Girls’ co-star Kat Dennings.

Zano and Dennings were spotted holding hands and cuddling up at the Los Angeles Lakers game this week.

On ‘Two Broke Girls’ they play love interests who haven’t gotten together yet, so maybe all the flirting on screen has lead to an off screen hook up.

Upgrade or downgrade?
